rigid pattern just like a fingerprint?
Or that catnip really is like a

00:00:07.799 --> 00:00:11.799
drug for cats?  One of its volatile
oils called nepetalactone enters

00:00:11.799 --> 00:00:16.209
the cats nasal tissue and acts like an
artificial cat pharamone.  The sensory neurons are

00:00:16.209 --> 00:00:19.740
stimulated and ultimately trigger a
