00:00:19.740 --> 00:00:24.019
brain and body in around 80%
of cats.  Which must be nice considering

00:00:24.019 --> 00:00:27.960
cats spend around 85%
of their day doing absolutely nothing.

00:00:27.960 --> 00:00:31.650
